bt_de: World temperatures could rise in the 21st century between 1.1 and 6.4 °C (2.0 and 11.5 °F) (Table 3). Sea level is likely to rise by 18 to 59 cm (7.08 to 23.22 in) [Table 3].

source: In reality Angle announced that he would be having neck surgery in May and would be out of action until August.
pivot_text(de): Angle sagte, dass er im Mai eine Halsoperation hatte und bis August außer Betrieb war.
pivot_text(zh): 事实上,Angle会在五月做颈部外科手术,因此,他要到八月才能行动。
bt_zh: In fact, Angle would have had a neck surgery in May, so he would not be able to operate until August.
bt_de: Angle said he had a neck surgery in May and was out of operation until August.

source: These flies are clothed in black or pale (white or golden) hairs, and are themselves either black or metallic green or blue.
pivot_text(de): Diese Fliegen haben schwarze oder blasse (weiße oder goldene) Haare. Sie sind entweder schwarz oder metallisch grün oder blau.
pivot_text(zh): 这些苍蝇染上黑色或浅色的彩色毛发,彩色是黑色或闪亮绿色/蓝色。
bt_zh: These flies have black or light coloured hair, which is black or bright green/blue.
bt_de: These flies have black or pale (white or golden) hair. They are either black or metallic green or blue.

source: Packaged instant soups come in several varieties: A packet of dry soup stock (like the ramen image below).
pivot_text(de): Verpackte Instant-Suppen kommen in verschiedenen Sorten, einschließlich Packungen von trockenen Suppen-Vorrat wie Ramen.
pivot_text(zh): 包装的即时汤以多种不同的方式涌现。 一包干汤储备(如下面的拉面图象) 。
bt_zh: Packaging instant soup emerges in a variety of different ways. A bag of dry soup reserves (a drawing image on the following side).
bt_de: Packed instant soups come in different varieties, including packs of dry soups stock like ramen.

source: Since 1980 the senior pastor has been John Piper.
